"4 pounds mustard greens (about 5 large bunches), large stems removed, greens coarsely chopped","4  to 5 tbsp. extra-virgin olive oil, divided","4  garlic cloves, minced","8  spring onions or 24 green onions, chopped","1/2  to 1 tsp. red chile flakes","1 teaspoon kosher salt","2 teaspoons cider vinegar"